graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        Controller[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Controller]
        Webhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Webhook]
        Manager[Manager<br/>Deployment]

        Manager -->|hosts| Controller
        Manager -->|hosts| Webhook
    end

    User[User/Data Scientist] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]

    NotebookCR -->|admission| Webhook
    Webhook -->|injects OAuth proxy| NotebookCR
    Webhook -->|adds reconciliation lock| NotebookCR

    NotebookCR -->|watched by| Controller

    Controller -->|creates| Route[OpenShift Route<br/>TLS Edge]
    Controller -->|creates| ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount<br/>OAuth annotations]
    Controller -->|creates| Secret[Secret<br/>OAuth config]
    Controller -->|creates| ConfigMap[ConfigMap<br/>Proxy config]
    Controller -->|creates| NetworkPolicy[NetworkPolicy<br/>Traffic control]

    subgraph "Notebook Pod"
        OAuthProxy[OAuth Proxy<br/>Sidecar Container]
        NotebookContainer[Notebook Container<br/>JupyterLab]
        OAuthProxy -->|localhost:8888| NotebookContainer
    end

    Route -->|routes traffic| OAuthProxy
    OAuthProxy -->|authenticates via| OpenShiftOAuth[OpenShift OAuth Server]
    OAuthProxy -->|authorizes via SAR| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API Server]

    Controller -->|depends on| KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller]
    Controller -->|depends on| OpenShiftRouteAPI[OpenShift Route API]
    Controller -->|depends on| ServiceCA[OpenShift Service CA Operator]

    ServiceCA -->|provisions certs| WebhookCert[Webhook TLS Cert]
    ServiceCA -->|provisions certs| OAuthCert[OAuth Proxy TLS Cert]

    style Controller fill:#4a90e2
    style Webhook fill:#4a90e2
    style Manager fill:#4a90e2
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623
    style KubeflowController fill:#999
    style OpenShiftRouteAPI fill:#999
    style ServiceCA fill:#7ed321
    style OpenShiftOAuth fill:#999
    style K8sAPI fill:#f5a623
    style OAuthProxy fill:#4a90e2
    style NotebookContainer fill:#4a90e2
